---
title: Korma and Mango Chutney Glazed Chicken Breast with Green Beans, Couscous and Tomato Salsa
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Korma and Mango Chutney Glazed Chicken Breast in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220927_R16_W45_UK_QR12203-8_MB_Main_12_low-7f349282.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/65ce498452f6e2fd05ccc79e.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/korma-and-mango-chutney-glazed-chicken-breast-65ce498452f6e2fd05ccc79e
servings: 2
course: main course
cuisine: Indian
author: HelloFresh
time required: 20 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 567 kcal
  fat: 13.4 g
  saturated fat: 4.4 g
  carbohydrates: 63.4 g
